<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('head', { 
        title: title, 
        description: description,
        lang: 'en',
        content: { title: title, metaDescription: description }
    }) %>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #fff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .privacy-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .privacy-container h1 {
            color: #333;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 2.5em;
        }
        .privacy-container h2 {
            color: #007bff;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }
        .privacy-container p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 1em;
        }
        .privacy-container ul {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .privacy-container li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .contact-info {
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .contact-info ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .contact-info li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        strong {
            color: #333;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('header', { lang: 'en' }) %>
    
    <div class="privacy-container">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> August 6, 2025</p>

        <div class="highlight">
            <p><strong>Important Notice:</strong> DotSave is a tool that allows users to download publicly available content from social media platforms. We do not host, store, or distribute any copyrighted content. All downloads are processed directly from the source platforms.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>DotSave collects minimal information to provide our service:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>URLs you submit:</strong> We temporarily process the URLs you provide to download content</li>
            <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> Basic analytics about how our service is used (anonymized)</li>
            <li><strong>Technical information:</strong> Browser type, device information, and IP address for service optimization</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the collected information solely for:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Processing your download requests</li>
            <li>Improving our service functionality</li>
            <li>Preventing abuse and ensuring service stability</li>
            <li>Complying with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Information Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties, except:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>When required by law or legal process</li>
            <li>To protect our rights and safety</li>
            <li>To prevent fraud or abuse of our service</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain your information only as long as necessary:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>URLs:</strong> Processed temporarily and not stored</li>
            <li><strong>Downloaded content:</strong> Never stored on our servers</li>
            <li><strong>Logs:</strong> Retained for 30 days for security purposes</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Request information about what data we have about you</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Opt out of analytics tracking</li>
            <li>Contact us with privacy concerns</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <p>We use minimal cookies for:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Essential service functionality</li>
            <li>Analytics to improve our service</li>
            <li>Preventing spam and abuse</li>
        </ul>
        <p>You can disable cookies in your browser settings, though this may affect service functionality.</p>

        <h2>7. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We may use third-party services for:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Analytics (Google Analytics)</li>
            <li>Advertising (Google AdSense)</li>
            <li>Content delivery networks</li>
        </ul>
        <p>These services have their own privacy policies.</p>

        <h2>8. Security</h2>
        <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>HTTPS encryption for all data transmission</li>
            <li>Regular security audits</li>
            <li>Limited data retention</li>
            <li>No storage of downloaded content</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>9. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our service is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent and believe your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us.</p>

        <h2>10. International Users</h2>
        <p>Our service is accessible worldwide. By using our service, you consent to the transfer of your information to and processing in countries where our servers are located.</p>

        <h2>11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify users of any material changes by posting the new policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.</p>

        <h2>12. DMCA Compliance</h2>
        <div class="highlight">
            <p><strong>Copyright Notice:</strong> DotSave respects intellectual property rights and complies with the Digital Millennium Copyright Act (DMCA).</p>
            <ul>
                <li>We do not host, store, or distribute copyrighted content</li>
                <li>All content is downloaded directly from source platforms</li>
                <li>We provide tools for users to download their own content or publicly available content</li>
                <li>We respond promptly to valid DMCA takedown notices</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <h2>13. Contact Information</h2>
        <div class="contact-info">
            <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our practices, please contact us:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> privacy@miconvert.com</li>
                <li><strong>DMCA Agent:</strong> dmca@miconvert.com</li>
                <li><strong>General Inquiries:</strong> support@miconvert.com</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> This Privacy Policy is effective as of August 6, 2025.</p>
    </div>
    
    <%- include('footer', { lang: 'en' }) %>
</body>
</html>
